---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout navTitle="幽影櫻與元的MC伺服器">



<main style="
        background-image: url('/Minecraft Screenshot 2025.06.26 - 01.23.07.95.png');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        height: 50vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        color: white;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    ">
    <!-- 標題文字 -->
    <div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 50px;">
        幽影櫻與元的Minecraft模組伺服器
    </div>
</main>

<div>
    &nbsp;
</div>

<div class="block">
        <!-- 伺服器位置 -->

    <div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px; text-align: center;">
        伺服器地址:
    </div>

    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; margin-top: 20px;">
        <div style="background-color: #1e1e1e; color: #ffffff; padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 8px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 18px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; ">

            <!-- 顯示伺服器地址 -->
            <div id="server-address" style="user-select: text;">mc.yuaner.tw</div>

            <!-- 複製按鈕 -->
            <button onclick="copyAddress()"
                    style="background-color: #333; color: white; border: none; padding: 5px 12px; font-size: 14px; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; width:4em ">
                複製
            </button>

        </div>
    </div>

    <script is:script>
        function copyAddress() {
            const text = document.getElementById("server-address").innerText;
            navigator.clipboard.writeText(text).then(() => {
                alert("已複製伺服器地址！");
            });
        }
    </script>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
        <p>
            <small>若主網址無法使用，請使用備用網址: mc-s2.yuaner.tw</small>
        </p>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: center; font-size: 20px;">
        <p>
            第一次遊玩前，請先去<a href="http://modpack.barian.moe">下載mainGUI模組同步程式</a>並執行過，將會自動下載所需模組，下載完成後即可開啟遊戲遊玩。
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="block"><!-- 主要內容 -->
    <!-- 原本的內容貼在這裡 -->





    <div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 30px; text-align: center;">
        伺服器介紹
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center; font-size: 20px;">
        <p>本頁面算是臨時官網先上線，先提供必要的下載資訊。目前我們已經大幅調整遊戲內容，相關介紹的話，之後有時間再慢慢完善吧～</p>

        <h3>相關連結</h3>
        <ul style="list-style-type: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;">
            <li>檔案資源下載：<a href="http://modpack.barian.moe">http://modpack.barian.moe</a></li>
            <li>客戶端同步後端：<a href="https://mc-api.yuaner.tw">https://mc-api.yuaner.tw</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

</Layout>

